---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Ecommerce Growth From Guernsey" description="Spires Digital is a founder-led ecommerce growth agency based in Guernsey, connecting acquisition, conversion, retention and measurement.">
  <div class="breadcrumbs-wrap"><Breadcrumbs items={[{ label: 'About' }]} /></div>
  <section class="about-hero hero-dark"><div class="container about-grid"><div><span class="badge">Founder-led from Guernsey</span><h1>Better marketing decisions start with commercial honesty.</h1></div><div class="about-intro"><p>Spires Digital exists to make ecommerce growth easier to understand and harder to fake. That means owned accounts, visible trade-offs and work measured against the economics of the business.</p><a href="/how-we-work" class="btn btn-outline btn-arrow">See how we work</a></div></div></section>

  <section class="section surface"><div class="container story-grid"><div class="founder-card"><div class="founder-mark">J</div><span>Founder-led agency</span><h2>Direct senior involvement.</h2><p>Jack leads the commercial and strategic work. Specialist support is brought in where the scope requires it, without adding unnecessary layers between the client and the decisions.</p><a href="mailto:jack@spiresdigital.com" class="text-link">jack@spiresdigital.com →</a></div><div class="story-copy"><span class="eyebrow">Why Spires Digital</span><h2>A reaction to the parts of agency life that do not help clients.</h2><p>After more than 15 years in digital marketing and over £10m in managed advertising spend, one pattern remained consistent: channel reporting can make activity look successful while the underlying business becomes less profitable.</p><p>Spires Digital was built around a different operating principle. Start with margin, customers and the commercial constraint. Use the right mix of acquisition, conversion, retention and measurement. Explain the evidence clearly. Keep the client in control.</p><p>The company is run from Guernsey and works with ecommerce brands across the UK and beyond through <strong>spiresdigital.com</strong>.</p></div></div></section>

  <section class="section values-section"><div class="container"><div class="section-heading"><span class="eyebrow">Operating principles</span><h2>What should remain true as the work gets more complex.</h2></div><div class="values-grid"><article><span>01</span><h3>Profit before platform credit</h3><p>Attributed revenue is a clue. Contribution, customer value and cash efficiency are the commercial outcome.</p></article><article><span>02</span><h3>Accounts stay yours</h3><p>Advertising, analytics and store data remain inside systems owned by your business.</p></article><article><span>03</span><h3>Evidence before certainty</h3><p>We distinguish what the data shows, what it suggests and what still needs to be tested.</p></article><article><span>04</span><h3>Useful communication</h3><p>Reporting should lead to a decision, not leave the reader searching for the point.</p></article><article><span>05</span><h3>No unnecessary lock-in</h3><p>Clear scopes and month-to-month working relationships keep accountability where it belongs.</p></article><article><span>06</span><h3>Specialism without silos</h3><p>Channels have different mechanics but share the same customer, economics and growth goal.</p></article></div></div></section>

  <section class="section surface"><div class="container certification-grid"><div><span class="eyebrow">Platform experience</span><h2>Practical experience across the ecommerce stack.</h2><p>Partnership badges are supporting evidence, not the proposition. The value is knowing how the platforms interact and where their reporting can mislead.</p></div><div class="cert-panel"><img src="/images/partners/shopify-partner.jpg" alt="Shopify Partner" loading="lazy" /><img src="/images/partners/awin-certified.png" alt="AWIN Certified Agency" loading="lazy" /><img src="/images/partners/meta-business-partner.avif" alt="Meta Business Partner" loading="lazy" /><img src="/images/partners/bing-partner.png" alt="Microsoft Advertising partner" loading="lazy" /></div></div></section>
  <section class="cta-section"><div class="container"><h2>Bring the growth question you cannot answer from a dashboard.</h2><p>We will start with the economics, the customer journey and the evidence already available.</p><a href="/contact" class="btn btn-white btn-lg btn-arrow">Start a useful conversation</a></div></section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-hero { padding-top: 5rem; }.about-grid { position: relative; z-index: 1; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.2fr .7fr; gap: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 7rem); align-items: end; }.about-intro p { margin: 0 0 1.5rem; }.story-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: .75fr 1.25fr; gap: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 7rem); align-items: start; }.founder-card { padding: 1.6rem; border-radius: var(--radius); background: var(--ink); color: #cbd2df; }.founder-mark { display: grid; width: 72px; height: 72px; place-items: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; border-radius: 18px; background: linear-gradient(135deg,var(--violet),var(--mint)); color: white; font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 850; }.founder-card > span { color: #91eadb; font-size: .68rem; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; }.founder-card h2 { margin: .8rem 0; color: white; font-size: 2rem; }.founder-card p { margin-bottom: 1.2rem; font-size: .87rem; }.founder-card .text-link { color: #91eadb; }.story-copy p { margin-top: 1.2rem; color: var(--slate); font-size: 1.05rem; }.values-section { background: #e9e8ff; }.values-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 1px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #d1cff9; border-radius: var(--radius); background: #d1cff9; }.values-grid article { min-height: 250px; padding: 1.5rem; background: #f7f6ff; }.values-grid article > span { color: var(--violet-dark); font-size: .7rem; font-weight: 800; }.values-grid h3 { margin: 2.5rem 0 .6rem; }.values-grid p { color: var(--slate); font-size: .84rem; }.certification-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: .8fr 1.2fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: center; }.certification-grid p { margin-top: 1rem; color: var(--slate); }.cert-panel { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); gap: 1rem; }.cert-panel img { width: 100%; height: 130px; padding: 1.2rem; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); object-fit: contain; filter: grayscale(1); }.cert-panel img:hover { filter: grayscale(0); }@media(max-width:850px){.about-grid,.story-grid,.certification-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.values-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}}@media(max-width:560px){.values-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
</style>
